data.description: Explore contemporary living in this 6-bed, 4-bath haven, boasting a 3-car tandem garage, nestled in a highly coveted neighborhood. Built in 2020, this residence offers convenience with proximity to amenities, shopping, and restaurants. The basement features 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom, while the upper level hosts 4 bedrooms. Utilize the flexible space for an office or additional living area. Enjoy the charm of a great backyard, completing the perfect blend of style and functionality. This home is minutes from Peterson SFB and 20 minutes from Fort Carson. Don’t miss this gorgeous gem complete with solar panels.
